#### Technical Data Report (TDR)
The `r prime_vs_sub` shall prepare and submit the "Technical Data Report" in accordance with CDRL `r TDR_CDRL_numb`. The "Technical Data Report" reports technical parameter data to provide context to the data reported in FlexFile submissions and to derive parametric cost estimating relationships.
